summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx detailing transportation charges for services rendered. It includes information about the shipment, billing details, and various service codes. The invoice indicates a total charge of $7.18 due by September 2, 2003.
keyFacts: Total charges amount to $7.18, due by September 2, 2003.
The shipment was picked up on August 6, 2003.
The document includes various service codes and descriptions related to FedEx services.
